    "doc": "Building and Running on PIC32MX Ethernet Starter Kit II",
    "title": "Building and Running the UDP Bootloader applications",
    "content": " ",
    "url": "http://localhost:4000/bootloader_apps_ethernet/apps/udp_bootloader/docs/readme_pic32mx_eth_sk2.html#building-and-running-the-udp-bootloader-applications",
